Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:06.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'd like to see Kudou-san.\NShe was hospitalized yesterday. Is it okay?{NOTE:ちょっと伺いします。あの、昨日入院した工藤さんに面会したいんですが、宜しいでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.96,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,Kudou-san? Oh, she's in room 301.{NOTE:工藤さんですね？三百一号室です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:どうも有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, this is all your fault!\NYou're supposed to be our captain!{NOTE:こずえ。全てはキャプテンのあなたのせいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.52,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's your fault!{NOTE:あなたのせいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Everyone's right. I'm to blame here.{NOTE:そうよ。あたしのせいだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:35.40,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I might've run away from Okei's checkup results yesterday, but today I won't.{NOTE:昨日は結果が恐ろしくて、おケイを見る前に逃げ出したけど、今日は逃げないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, it's here.{NOTE:あ、あつこだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.91,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,Please let me through!{NOTE:ちょっと退いて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me…!{NOTE:ま、まさか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei…!{NOTE:おケイが…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. But…{NOTE:よかった。でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.35,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.{NOTE:はい、どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.65,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Wah, captain!{NOTE:ま、キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei, you're up?{NOTE:おケイ、一体。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.36,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I'm being discharged.{NOTE:ふふ。あのね、これからXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Really!? Oh, I'm so happy for you!{NOTE:ま、よかった。よかったわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.41,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry about me, captain.{NOTE:ごめんね、キャプテン。色々心配かけちゃって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Don't be.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.33,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,We must apologize.{NOTE:あ、いつぞや失礼しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.00,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Keiko has caused you a lot of trouble.{NOTE:けいこが皆さんにしっかりご面倒をおかけしまして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Actually, it's the other way around.{NOTE:いいえ、こちらこそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Because of me, Keiko-san ended up in the\hhospital. How can I ever apologize to you?{NOTE:けいこさんを入院させるような事してしまって、なんとお詫びして良いのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:46.97,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,There's nothing to apologize for. Keiko has always had a weak heart. She just never told anyone.{NOTE:お詫びだなんて…もともと心臓が弱かったんですってそれを知らずに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:51.35,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,If I were to continue playing volleyball, I'd probably be risking my life.{NOTE:これからもね、バレーを続ければ、命を保証しないとって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I-It's that bad?{NOTE:え？そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:57.07,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I feel like I was given a death sentence.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.19,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,After all, I love volleyball so much.{NOTE:だって、あたしバレーが大好きだったんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.45,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,So, I've made up my mind.{NOTE:それでさっぱり決心したの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Really? So, you'll…{NOTE:決心？じゃ、バレー部を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.08,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,…not quit the club, of course.{NOTE:もちろん止めないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I see…{NOTE:え…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.45,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I'll become the manager.{NOTE:マネージャーよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.17,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Just because I can't play doesn't mean I can't be of use to the volleyball club.{NOTE:プレーができなくても、バレー部の役に立ちたいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's great, Okei!{NOTE:偉いわ、おケイ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.88,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's a really good idea.{NOTE:そこまでよく思いきれたわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I really am.{NOTE:よかった。本当に良かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:30.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I'm also a little jealous of Okei.{NOTE:割り切っておケイXXXがちょっぴり羨ましいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:35.10,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I didn't have he heart to tell her that I'm not the captain anymore.{NOTE:おケイには黙ってたけど、私はもうキャプテンでも何でもないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.69,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei might've found her way back in.{NOTE:おケイのことは解決したとしても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.45,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I can't go back after the way I was treated.{NOTE:私は素直に合宿戻ることなんかできないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:49.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Now that I know what the girls think of me.{NOTE:あたしはバレー部員皆の気持ちを知らされたんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But even so, I just can't throw volleyball away.{NOTE:でも、私はバレーを捨てることなんてできやしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:03.22,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to try and regain my team's and professor Hongou's trust.{NOTE:そうすれば、もう一度皆をそして本郷先生を信頼するしかないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.26,Alternative,Oohara,0,0,0,,Trust is everything. You need to go hand in hand.{NOTE:信頼よ。心と心が通わなければだめ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:14.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Just because I am no longer their captain doesn't mean I need to step down altogether.{NOTE:キャプテンとして裏切られたからといって、バレーを止めるとは言われてないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,They still need me for the All-Japan championship.{NOTE:全国優勝のためには私が必要なことくらい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,They'll realize that as soon as they calm down a bit.{NOTE:皆だって冷静になれば分かることだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And when they do, professor Hongou will see it, too.{NOTE:そうすれば、本郷先生だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.19,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.28,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.16,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:27.82,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.57,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What's that,\Nwhat's that?{NOTE:どうした、どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.37,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.53,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{NOTE:—いくぞう。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.66,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{NOTE:—しっかり取れ。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.95,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:触れ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.79,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Don't sleep.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—ほら、もたもたするな。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.71,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.75,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Once more!{NOTE:もう一つ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.25,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.50,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Here goes!{NOTE:いくぞ、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.26,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Got it!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:44.92,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All right, attention!{NOTE:皆、聞け。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Listen. Tomorrow we're playing the qualifier finals.{NOTE:いいか？明日は予選の決勝だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.18,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,And yet, what's with that form?{NOTE:このXXなんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.64,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,You expect to win the championship this way?{NOTE:こんなことでは全国選手権大会の優勝はおるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,At this rate, even the qualifiers are at risk.{NOTE:予選に勝ち抜くことさえ危ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.69,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Show some effort.{NOTE:もっとXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.02,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,But professor.{NOTE:でも、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:02.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.69,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Well…{NOTE:あの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What is it? Say it already.{NOTE:なんだ？言ってみろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.11,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Well, can we really win without Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:あの。鮎原さんがいなくて、勝てるんでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.49,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,I'm really worried about it.{NOTE:とても不安です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Fufu.{NOTE:うふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Looks like they acknowledge my skill.{NOTE:あたしの実力は認めてるらしいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Let's make one thing clear right now.{NOTE:では、はっきり言おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.{NOTE:心配することはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:25.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,We don't need Ayuhara. You all have what it takes to win without her.{NOTE:鮎原がいなくても、君達は十分に勝てる実力を持っているんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou!{NOTE:本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's right. It's just like professor says, girls.{NOTE:そうよ。ね、皆。先生のおっしゃる通りだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:35.02,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Even without Kozue, we can definitely win with our skills.{NOTE:こずえはいなくても、今のあたしたちの実力なら絶対勝てるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.02,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Yup.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:37.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:42.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou thinks nothing of me.{NOTE:本郷先生が私のことなんか何とも思ってないんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,They don't care about my feelings at all.{NOTE:あたしの気持ちなんてどうでも良いのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:48.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm… I'm just a fifth wheel to them.{NOTE:あたしは、あたしは余計者の部員なのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.79,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Captain!\N– Ah?{NOTE:—キャプテン！\\N—あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.25,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Captain…{NOTE:キャプテン…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.17,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Oh, Okei!\N– Okei!{NOTE:—あ、おケイ！\\N—おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.76,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.55,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,And that's why I'd like to become a manager from today on.{NOTE:そういうわけであたしは今日からマネージャーにして欲しいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:そうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:15.26,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It must've been hard to hear that you won't be able to play anymore.{NOTE:や、バレーが出来ないという宣告は辛かったろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But I'm glad you didn't let it get to you, Kudou.{NOTE:でも、くどう。よくそこまで決心したな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.77,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Hehe.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.81,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Anyway.{NOTE:そうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:24.77,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Currently our volleyball club has no manager, so Kudou will fill that position nicely.{NOTE:現在我がバレー部にはマネージャーがいないが、なるほど工藤なら適任だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.48,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.78,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,By the way, I saw captain just now.{NOTE:あの、今キャプテンに会ったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ehm.\N– Oh?{NOTE:—ん。\\N—へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.86,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,What is it, girls?{NOTE:どうしたの、皆？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.91,Default,Ooki,0,0,0,,You see, Ayuhara-san…{NOTE:だって、あたしたちは鮎原さんのこと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.95,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,We had a fight and she's no longer our captain.{NOTE:誤解して、追い出したような形になっちゃったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.12,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.58,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Say what?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.25,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,So that's why the captain looked like that.{NOTE:それでキャプテンの様子が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.30,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,What the heck, girls!?\NKozue is suffering and you just let it be?{NOTE:ちょっと、皆！よく調べもしないで、XXXの人達だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,You're right. You're completely right.{NOTE:そうよ。その通りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit Kozue and apologize to her.{NOTE:あたし、これからこずえの家へ、謝ってくるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.39,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Me too.{NOTE:あたしも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.85,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,I'll go as well.{NOTE:私も行くわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.02,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,No, it's no use.{NOTE:いや、だめだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:02.27,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara won't be returning to the volleyball club.{NOTE:君たち鮎原もうバレー部には戻ってこないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.{NOTE:そ、そんなことありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.86,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,If we honestly apologize, I'm sure she'll come around.{NOTE:心から謝れば、きっと分かってくれると思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.61,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go.{NOTE:そうよ。行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It's pointless.{NOTE:無駄だね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You want me to join the gymnastics club?{NOTE:あたしは先生の体操部へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.49,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Yes. Under these circumstances, saying it's a good opportunity might sound strange.{NOTE:え。そう言う事情なら良い機会と言うのは変だけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.66,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,But I'd definitely welcome you in our club.{NOTE:ぜひあなたを体操部で迎えたいと思うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But—{NOTE:でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.00,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,The members will surely be thrilled as well.{NOTE:体操部員達もきっと大歓迎よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:31.59,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,If you can let go of volleyball, you're bound to succeed in the gymnastics club.{NOTE:あなたがバレーに見切りを付けられれば、体操部も活気が出てくるんだけれど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,They did make themselves clear about it.{NOTE:たった今はっきり知らされたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm no longer needed in the volleyball club.{NOTE:私はバレー部に必要の無い人間だって言うこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:44.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't think I can quit volleyball.{NOTE:でも私にはバレーを止めることは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.73,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,We don't need Ayuhara. You all have what it takes to win without her.{NOTE:鮎原がいなくても十分勝てる出力を持っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.98,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's right. Even without Kozue, we can definitely win.{NOTE:そうよ。こずえがいなくても勝てるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.07,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Still…{NOTE:そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even though I love volleyball I\hdon't want anything to do with that club.{NOTE:私はバレーを捨てることはできなくても、こんなバレー部は嫌だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We don't go hand in hand at all.{NOTE:心の通い合いなんてどこにもないんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The most important thing in team play is missing.{NOTE:チームプレーで一番大切なものが欠けてるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.79,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.04,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You don't have to respond right away.{NOTE:決心が付かなければ、今すぐでなくても良いのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No. I made up my mind already.{NOTE:いいえ。ご返事します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor Nakajima, please let me join the gymnastics club.{NOTE:中島先生、私を体操部へ入れてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:17.18,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Really? That was quick, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:そう？やっと決心してくれたのね、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.05,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,I'm glad.{NOTE:よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oohara-senpai, I'm sorry.{NOTE:大原先輩、ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:26.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I no longer have the strength to remain in the volleyball club.{NOTE:私にはこれ以上バレー部に止まる勇気がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.61,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,– Hey, it's Ayuhara-san.\N– Eh?{NOTE:—ね、鮎原さんよ。\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She's talking to miss Nakajima of the gymnastics club.{NOTE:体操部の中島先生と話してるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What if she…?{NOTE:もしかしたら、こずえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.24,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,N-No way, she's joining the gymnastics club?{NOTE:ま、まさか体操部に？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.49,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Let's go and see.{NOTE:行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.91,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,All right, come to the gymnastics club tomorrow morning.{NOTE:じゃ、明日の朝体操部に来てね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okay, I will.{NOTE:はい。分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.71,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll make a fresh start with the gymnastics club.{NOTE:私はもう一度体操部でやり直すわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Just like Izumi-san.{NOTE:あの泉さんのように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.89,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, we just met Okei. I'm sorry.{NOTE:こずえ、何もかもおケイに聞いたわ。ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We misunderstood each other.{NOTE:あたしたち誤解してたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.43,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,So, we want to apologize to you.{NOTE:だから、あなたには謝りたくてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's all right.{NOTE:ん、もういいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't think anything of it.{NOTE:誤解だなんて、私何とも思ってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.48,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Really? That's great!{NOTE:本当？良かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.73,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,So then you'll return to the volleyball club?{NOTE:じゃ、バレー部に戻ってくれるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:17.61,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,We're all so anxious without you there.{NOTE:やっぱり、あなたがいないとあたしたちは不安なのよ。だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Well, it's too late for that.{NOTE:でももう遅いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:22.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I've just joined the gymnastics club.{NOTE:私はたった今体操部の人間になって出発するのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Y-You didn't!{NOTE:そ、そんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's official.{NOTE:もういいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:30.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am praying for you all to become stronger and win the All-Japan championship.{NOTE:今以上に強くなって、全国優勝してくれることを祈ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.96,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Well, that sucks.{NOTE:そ、そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hey! You girls!{NOTE:こら！君たち！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.26,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What happened to your practice?{NOTE:練習もX何をしているんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But, professor.{NOTE:でも、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.60,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I give you one finger and you bite off the whole hand.{NOTE:ちょっと褒めてやれば、すぐに逆上せて、この始末だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.81,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten about tomorrow?{NOTE:こんなことじゃ全国優勝は居るか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,We need to drill for the tomorrow's qualifiers.{NOTE:明日の予選で代表になることさいをXX付かないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.02,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do you understand?{NOTE:分かったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Are you deaf?{NOTE:君たちはつんぼか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Get back to the court. Right now.{NOTE:速くコートへ戻れ。練習だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Now!{NOTE:速く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.41,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes. – Okay.{NOTE:—は、はい。\\N—はい。—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.91,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, I just have one thing to ask you.{NOTE:こずえ。あなたに一つだけ聞きたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.42,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Can… can you really let go of volleyball?{NOTE:あなた、あなた…本当にバレーを止められるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm part of the gymnastics club now.{NOTE:私は体操部の人間よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's all?{NOTE:それだけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's your answer?{NOTE:それが答えなのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Fine…{NOTE:よく分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.85,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'll pray for your success in the gymnastics club.{NOTE:体操部でのあなたの活躍を祈ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori. It's cruel to ask me a question like that.{NOTE:みどり。私にバレーを止められたなんて…残酷な質問だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I've already made a decision, though.{NOTE:でもあたしにだって意地がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:38.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I still don't want to see you lose to Fukuoka.{NOTE:ただ、福岡中に負けたと思うと残念だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:42.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But that's volleyball club and professor Hongou's problem now.{NOTE:でも、それはバレー部員皆の、そして本郷先生のせいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, look at me.{NOTE:あ、ばかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Still worrying about the volleyball club's issues even though I'm no longer its member.{NOTE:バレー部員じゃないのに。負けようXどうしようXあたしのしたことじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the gymnastics club now.{NOTE:あたしは体操部の人間ですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The volleyball club has nothing to do with me anymore.{NOTE:あんなバレー部なんてXXXなればいいんだわ。}
Comment: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:02.05,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Good morning. Did you sleep well?{NOTE:皆。よく眠れたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.73,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Well, today is the qualifiers final.{NOTE:さて、今日はいよいよ予選の決勝だが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.28,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Let's keep in high spirits and win.{NOTE:その元気で優勝をいただく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.15,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:いいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.03,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.{NOTE:では、出発。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.70,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san…?{NOTE:鮎原さん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.29,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,In the end, she didn't come.{NOTE:やっぱり来なかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Okei.{NOTE:おケイ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Why did you think that Kozue would come?{NOTE:あなたどうしてこずえは来ると思うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.92,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Because…{NOTE:だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue joined the gymnastics club.{NOTE:こぜうは体操部に移ったのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd come.{NOTE:来るわけがないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We can win even without Kozue!{NOTE:こずえはいなくだって、優勝はできるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Whoa.\N– Huh?{NOTE:—ま。\\N—ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.19,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Good morning, professor.{NOTE:先生。おはようございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.61,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Listen, you're a member of the gymnastics club from today on.{NOTE:いいこと。今日からあなたは体操部の人間なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.{NOTE:はい。分かってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see them off.{NOTE:ただちょっとバスを見かけたので。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.16,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:もういいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.08,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone is waiting.{NOTE:さ、皆が待ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.50,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You'll be the most talented newcomer our club has ever had.{NOTE:体操部の最も有能な新人わね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.71,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,One-two-three.{NOTE:一二三。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.25,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Two-two-three.{NOTE:二二三。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.84,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Three-two-three.{NOTE:三二三。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.46,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Girls, let me introduce Ayuhara-san. She'll be joining our club today.{NOTE:—四二三。\\N—皆さん。今日から体操部に入った鮎原さんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.{NOTE:どうぞよろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.26,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Nice to meet you.\N– Nice to meet you.{NOTE:—よろしく。\\N—よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:29.39,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,A volleyball team's captain joins our club? Terrific!{NOTE:バレー部XX体操部に入るなんて素敵！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:33.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,This is the first time I'll be doing gymnastics, so please be patient with me.{NOTE:体操は初めてなんですもの。XXお願いするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.52,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:でも、鮎原さんのことですもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.15,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,You'll surely lead us to victory in all of our contests.{NOTE:今度は体操もきっと優勝させてくれるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, please.{NOTE:あ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.61,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough.{NOTE:はい、それまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.23,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Time for practice.{NOTE:さ、練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.70,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,– I assume you're warmed up.\N– Yes ma'am. – Yes ma'am.{NOTE:—準備体操はいいよね。\\N—はい。はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.61,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Let's start with leg spreads.{NOTE:じゃ、まず開脚。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.91,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Go with the jump.{NOTE:飛び越しから初め。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.70,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.50,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Okay, next.{NOTE:はい、次。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.50,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.42,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san has joined our club.{NOTE:鮎原さんが入ってのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.47,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,It seems to have motivated everyone.{NOTE:皆やる気を起こしたみたいだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.68,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.76,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.47,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Try not to make a spectacle.{NOTE:いいとこ見せようX考えたらだめ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.18,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Try again, this time higher.{NOTE:もう一度。はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:14.85,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.60,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's tough.{NOTE:厳しいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:22.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The always-kind professor Nakajima feels like a completely different person.{NOTE:あの優しい中島先生とは別人みたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.57,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Next.{NOTE:次。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:28.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,This is no joke. I have to work hard in this club.{NOTE:そうだは。私はこの体操部で一生懸命やらなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:33.16,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,While I am good at volleyball, I don't want to admit that I'm poor at gymnastics.{NOTE:バレーは上手だけど、体操はからっきし下手だなんて言われたくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.12,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Especially not to Midori.{NOTE:特にみどり達には。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.71,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san. Try it out yourself.{NOTE:鮎原さん。やってごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I will show to everyone that\NI can succeed in this club, too.{NOTE:私が体操部でも立派にやれるって事を見せてあげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.69,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,How skillful.{NOTE:上手いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.56,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,As expected from Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:さすがには鮎原さんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, it's just beginner's luck.{NOTE:いやだわ。Xよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.73,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,So-so, I guess.{NOTE:まま、ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.78,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Okay, let's move on to the next exercise.{NOTE:さ。次に移りましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.62,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Good, do not lose the balance.{NOTE:そう。バランスをしっかり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:16.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.62,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Try it once more.{NOTE:さ、もう一度。やり直し。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.55,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Stretch out and turn your back.{NOTE:ピンと伸ばして、背中をはい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.46,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,That's it.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:36.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm actually doing pretty well in the gymnastics club.{NOTE:XXX違う体操部での厳しい練習あたしは夢中で頑張った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:40.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even though I was forced to face new exercises without having time to catch up.{NOTE:そして引っ付く暇もなく、新しい練習に挑戦させられた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.95,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Redo.{NOTE:さ、もう一度。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I was already absorbed.{NOTE:私はもう無我夢中だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I was trying to forget about volleyball, about Midori, and about professor Hongou.{NOTE:バレーのことも、みどりのことも、本郷先生のことも忘れて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou!?{NOTE:本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.51,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What's up? How are things at the gymnastics club?{NOTE:おい。どうだ？体操部の感想は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"How are things"?{NOTE:背徳の感想ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, professor, but that's none of your business anymore.{NOTE:私がどうなろうと先生には全然関係ないことでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.69,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hehehe.{NOTE:へへへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.77,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Don't be so cold, now.{NOTE:おい、おい。そう邪険にするなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:32.74,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,We won the qualifiers, so I thought it would be nice to let you know.{NOTE:や、今日の予選に勝てたので、一応君に知らせておこうと思ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:36.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Is that so? Well, you didn't have to go out your way just to inform me.{NOTE:そうですか？わざわざ知らせてくださらなくて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But congratulations, I guess.{NOTE:ま、いちおめでとういますわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,You seem to have held a grudge against me for quite a while. Huh?{NOTE:きみは随分僕のことを憎んでいるらしいな。え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, you could tell?{NOTE:お分かりになりますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:50.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's just that I didn't think that you were such a cold person.{NOTE:先生があんなに冷たい人だなと思ってなかったんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You knew very well what volleyball meant to me.{NOTE:あたしだって、どんなにバレーを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Well, you might not like to hear this.{NOTE:ま、君にはいいにくいんだが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.76,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But Hayakawa does well in your place.{NOTE:早川は君の分までよくやってくれている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Same goes to the rest of the girls on the team.{NOTE:それに、他のバレー部の皆も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:05.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,We will be able to win the All-Japan championship, even without you.{NOTE:君がいなくても全日本選手権で優勝してみせるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.31,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,We're pretty good, wouldn't you say?{NOTE:中々XX持っているよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You came here just to tell me that?{NOTE:そんなこと私に言うために先生は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:16.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,How is it, by the way?\NGymnastics is said to be pretty difficult.{NOTE:どうだ？体操と言うのは難しいもんだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.66,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I don't think that it will go as well for you as it did in the volleyball club.{NOTE:いくら君XXって、バレーのようにはいかないだろな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It will, professor.{NOTE:先生、あたしやります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You know that I achieve my goals. I'll prove I can succeed in this new club as well.{NOTE:意志にかじりついたって、体操で優勝してみせるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:32.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's right. I'll show you and everyone in the volleyball club that I can succeed.{NOTE:そうよ。きっと優勝して、本郷先生とバレー部の皆に見せつけてあげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.67,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,That's it. That's the spirit.{NOTE:そうだ。その意気だと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.88,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara. You can surely do it.{NOTE:鮎原。君ならきっとできる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.51,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Good luck, Ayuhara.{NOTE:頑張れよ、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I want to play volleyball.{NOTE:私はバレーをやりたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:49.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But professor Hongou and the volleyball club members are now my enemies.{NOTE:でもバレー部も信じていた本郷先生も今は皆敵。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The club has done just fine without me.{NOTE:私の考えたバレーも独り善がりの理想だったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.45,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.66,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.16,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.74,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Why are you holding back?{NOTE:どうして遠慮するの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Everyone's slacking.{NOTE:皆弛んでるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:09.29,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori. It isn't the best time to say it, but things are bad.{NOTE:ね、みどり。今頃なってこんなこと言っちゃう、悪いんだけどさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What is it? Be specific.{NOTE:何なの？さっさと言ったらどう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.80,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,The All-Japan championship starts tomorrow, right?{NOTE:明日からは全国大会、でしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.59,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,And to be honest, we're still all worried that we can't win without Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:つまり、鮎原さんがいなくて勝てるかどうか心配なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What? Why are you bringing this up now?{NOTE:ま、今更何を言い出すの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say I'm incompeten—{NOTE:私が役不足だって言うわけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.14,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Far from it.{NOTE:そんな意味じゃないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.60,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,We're just anxious.{NOTE:あたしたちは不安なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:28.23,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Also without Ayuhara-san,\NI feel like we lost our power.{NOTE:それに、鮎原さんがいないと、何だか力が抜けたみたいでさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.65,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Didn't it feel like each of us played alone, instead of as a team?{NOTE:チームプレーだって何となくバラバラみたいな感じがしない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.11,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I felt it from the very beginning.{NOTE:そのことは私が一番初めに感じていたこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.20,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We may have won the match today.{NOTE:今日の決勝戦は今までの勢いで買ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.53,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid of what comes next.{NOTE:でも今は不安。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.83,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,For the first time, I realize the weight of responsibility a captain carries.{NOTE:キャプテンとは以下に責任X重いX初めて分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.71,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's a deep internal struggle.{NOTE:それは厳しい自分との戦い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.84,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I think I understand now the feelings that Kozue hid behind her hard training.{NOTE:こずえのハードトレーニングをXXXってきた気持ちがよく分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:58.84,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Even when everyone blames you, you're still expected to push forward.{NOTE:その時は非難されても、後で必ず来てくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:04.35,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Even when no one understood her, Kozue believed in everyone and pushed the team to its limits.{NOTE:誰も分かってくれるない中でこずえは皆を信じて一人で憎まれXXXしてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.35,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Midori?{NOTE:みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She may still be there.{NOTE:まだいるかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.73,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Ah, Midori! Where are you going?{NOTE:あ、みどり、どこへ行くの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,To the gymnastics club.{NOTE:体操部よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Wait, Hayakawa.{NOTE:待て、早川。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:18.07,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Before you go see Ayuhara, let me relay you her words.{NOTE:鮎原の所行く前に。鮎原の言葉を伝えよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara said:{NOTE:相原はこう言ったぞ：}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:26.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,If you go to Tōkyō without me, you will lose in the very first set.{NOTE:自分がいなければ、東京へ行っても、第一線で絶対負けるに決まってるってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.29,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,I can't believe Ayuhara-san said such thing.{NOTE:鮎原さんがそんなこと言うなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.88,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara now belongs to the gymnastics club.{NOTE:鮎原は今体操部の人間だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,She's aiming for success in that club.{NOTE:その体操部での優勝を目指している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:いいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara's full of confidence.{NOTE:これは鮎原自信な欠けた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It is a new challenge from her.{NOTE:挑戦の言葉だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,A challenge?{NOTE:挑戦？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:47.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Yes. Ayuhara thinks that without her, the\hself-proclaimed star, our club will weaken.{NOTE:つまり、鮎原は自分と言うスターが抜けたバレー部はガタガタだと思っているんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:51.85,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do you still intend to chase Ayuhara after hearing this, Hayakawa?{NOTE:そこまでに下げられても、早川。君は鮎原をかけているのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.15,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Indeed, Kozue declared herself to be a part of the gymnastics club now.{NOTE:確かにこずえは体操部の人間と言った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:59.03,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I wonder if she joined that club just to become a star again?{NOTE:こずえは自分なスターでやってる受ける場所を求めているのかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.95,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,At any rate, I will not forgive her mocking our volleyball club.{NOTE:でも、バレー部を侮辱する気持ちだけは許せない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.99,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What is it, Hayakawa?{NOTE:どうした、早川？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do you still want to go cry on Ayuhara's shoulder about your lack of confidence?{NOTE:自身がないなら、今から鮎原に泣きついてもいいんだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.96,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind.{NOTE:あたし考え直しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.00,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Really?{NOTE:そうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.50,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I hope it's not all about pride.{NOTE:プライドなら関係ないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:20.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's partly a reason too. However, I\hrealized that depending on others is a mistake.{NOTE:それもあります。でも、それより他人に頼ろうとした甘えた考え方が間違っていたと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Listen, girls.{NOTE:いい、皆？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:27.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,All of us will win on the merit of our own strength!{NOTE:あたしたちバレー部はあたしたちだけの力で絶対に優勝勝ち取るのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.60,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All right. That's the spirit!{NOTE:よし。その意気だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.35,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Go for it, girls!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—頑張れ、皆！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:35.40,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,The All-Japan championships…\Nthis is my own chance to become a star.{NOTE:全国優勝。それこそ私のスターに成るチャンス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.57,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You're pretty early, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:早いのね、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.91,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You look a bit lonely.{NOTE:なんだか寂しそうだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.49,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Your friends went to Tōkyō, you must miss them.{NOTE:バレー部は皆東京へ行ったからでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, everything's all right.{NOTE:いいえ。何でもありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.46,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You won't fool me.{NOTE:痩せ我慢ね。ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.75,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Ah, never mind.{NOTE:まいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:58.00,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Anyway, Ayuhara-san.\NIn the next three days, we're going…{NOTE:所で鮎原さん。あなたは今日から三日間で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.84,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,…to have you master the forward, backward and sideways somersault.{NOTE:…前後左右の空中回転をマスターしてもらうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Forward, backward and sideways?{NOTE:前後左右の空中回転ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:04.76,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.09,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You can already do a front walk over on the beam.{NOTE:あなたはすでに腕立て回転ができるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.26,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,The next step is to learn the somersaults.{NOTE:今度は空中回転よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to learn it in just three days?{NOTE:三日間でって言うのはどう言うことですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And why somersaults specifically?{NOTE:それにまたなぜ前後左右の空中回転を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.60,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,You'll understand it soon.{NOTE:いずれ分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:19.48,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,But I did make a bet with professor Hongou.{NOTE:とにかく、本郷先生に約束をしたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou?{NOTE:本郷先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.94,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Actually, professor Hongou said:{NOTE:実はね、本郷先生が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:28.66,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,"No matter how good Ayuhara was at our club, she can't do gymnastics."{NOTE:「鮎原はいくらバレーが出来たからって、体操部では通用しないだろう」なって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What? How cruel!{NOTE:ま。そんなこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.33,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,This is where I stepped in.{NOTE:だからは宣言したの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:37.08,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,"I will prove you are mistaken and show you that she can master somersaults in just three days."{NOTE:「そんなにおっしゃるなら、難しい空中回転を三日間でマスターさせます」って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:42.67,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,I think I might have said too much, though.{NOTE:つまらないこと言ったなった思うかもしれないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:45.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, he insulted us.{NOTE:いいえ。侮辱されたんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.93,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Anyway, I let the other girls rest for three days.{NOTE:とにかく。三日間は体操部員を休ませたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.93,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,We'll hold a special training for you.{NOTE:だから、あなた一人の特訓よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.27,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Please prepare yourself.{NOTE:覚悟してちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.98,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start right now.{NOTE:じゃ、早速練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:59.56,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,The most important part is to take a good first step.{NOTE:大切なのは思い切って踏み切ること。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.56,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Got it?\N– Yes ma'am.{NOTE:—いいわね？\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.32,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Begin!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:06.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.07,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,That was a good fall.{NOTE:XXXが上手いわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Redo.\N– Yes ma'am.{NOTE:—さ、もう一度。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.83,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Use the whole body.{NOTE:体の力を抜いて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.08,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Once more.\N– Yes ma'am.{NOTE:—はい、もう一度。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.75,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Watch your timing. Make it quicker.{NOTE:タイミング取って。もっと速く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:26.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,For some reason, I feel like I'm being manipulated.{NOTE:私は何だか鳥XX人形みたいにXX気がする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:28.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I'll go along with it anyway.{NOTE:どう考えても、やめないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:30.68,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What's the true meaning behind this exercise?{NOTE:この練習にはなにかある？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:31.93,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:34.85,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,The famous volleyball club's captain is down with just this?{NOTE:バレー部のキャプテンとまろ人がこれしきでこれしきでダウンなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:37.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,N-Not at all.{NOTE:や、やります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:40.56,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Then hurry and stand up.{NOTE:さ、だったら早く立って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,T-This is nothing.{NOTE:こ、こんなことで負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.99,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,Looks like we can make it.{NOTE:これなら三日間できっと上手く行くわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:54.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara family{NOTE:鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:05.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"Fujimi Academy adds the first game to its track record."{NOTE:富士見学園第一戦を飾る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:10.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"Fukuoka Middle School wins its first match by a shutout."{NOTE:期待の強豪福岡中も第一せんをシャットアウト。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:14.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,At this rate Fujimi Academy might lose.{NOTE:このままでは富士見学園の優勝は難しいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What am I saying? I have decided not to worry about the volleyball club.{NOTE:何をいまさら？バレー部に見れは持たないで決心したはずよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am going to focus on mastering the somersault in three days.{NOTE:あたしは三日間で空中回転をマスターすることがさしあたっての目的。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.{NOTE:でも分からないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There has to be some point to it.{NOTE:きっとこれには理由があるはずよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:45.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Something's up.{NOTE:きっと何が意味XXよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:48.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And not knowing what it is frustrates me.{NOTE:それがはっきりしないなんて悔しいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:49.42,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll keep enduring it, though.{NOTE:でも負けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,How can I not?{NOTE:へこたれるもんか。}
Comment: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:55.43,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:01.31,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,The All-Japan volleyball championship games begin.{NOTE:全国バレーボール選手権大会は華やかに開幕し。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:03.81,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy wins the first round.{NOTE:富士見学園は一回戦に楽勝。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:08.19,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Kozue puts up a solitary fight at the gymnastics club.{NOTE:一方、こずえは一人体操部で孤独な戦いを続けている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:14.32,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,She quickly grows to hate the challenge of learning multiple kinds of somersaults on such a short notice.{NOTE:三日間でマスターXXという空中回転に憎しみにも似た激しされこずえは挑戦する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:18.99,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,It's only then when the rivaling Fukuoka Middle School shows off their true power in Tōkyō.{NOTE:そのごろ、東京ではライバル福岡中の活躍が一息は目立っていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:22.83,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンはお楽しみに。}
